ps%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhikunet.com%2Fuploads%2Fvod%2F2019-05-27%2F5cebffaa460c2.jpg&h=fd42f78d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.char.tw/uploads/20190306062205_61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.char.tw%2Fuploads%2F20190306062205_61.jpg&h=47c9dabf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://kalselpos.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Captain-Marvel-001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkalselpos.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2FCaptain-Marvel-001.jpg&h=f3821f0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://joseph-morris.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/captain-marvel-gif-7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjoseph-morris.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2Fcaptain-marvel-gif-7.gif&h=3930e186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.麥克&middot;福隆（斯科特&middot;阿金斯飾），號稱意外殺手的他，是位冷血殺手。就他從事的職業來講，他是頂尖的，無論是條理多樣的刺殺技巧，還是瞞天過海躲過警察視線，他的每次任務都使雇主滿意高興。但是有一天他摯愛的人卻捲入了倫敦的地下殺手世界，並慘遭自己同組織的人殺害。而福隆不得不打破自己長久以來井然有序，條理安排的生活，開始向實施這一切的人展開復仇<br />\n<br />\n2.Scott Adkins飾演的囚犯得到假釋的機會，於是他找准時機甩掉負責監視的警察，從而繼續他的複仇之路，讓仇人血債血償。同時藉此機會尋找多年前早已迷失的自我，實現自我救贖。 <br />\n<br />\n3.1995年，克里帝國星際部隊成員佛斯在首都哈拉星進行訓練，她困惑於被清除記憶而難以控制自身情緒及能量，所屬部隊指揮官楊羅格與克里AI統治者「至高智慧」因此不斷告誡教誨她。楊羅格的部隊受命前往邊境星球托法星，試圖尋找失蹤的克里人臥底，卻掉入敵對的史克魯爾人所設下的圈套。佛斯被史克魯爾人將軍塔洛斯擄走，楊羅格與其他成員被逼撤退。史克魯爾人在太空船內以記憶讀取裝置收集佛斯腦中的情報，使她回想起片段的零碎記憶。佛斯用超能力脫困成功並試圖逃離，最後她所乘的逃生艙被塔洛斯攻擊毀損，從太空墜至鄰近星球C-53（地球）<br />\n<br />\n12 50AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2Kd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=65b5015c\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2Kd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=d38c7be1\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e034121f0beb3debb9061ec6e34f07ee5d38cc","tid":1175632,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T16:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0257544f22369dfae3c9ce4cb1bb5738f48d12b","tid":1175632,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T17:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ab3e7d949f5642d2e19bb26b08956da60c107f","tid":1175632,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T18:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46738ec55a10572e9a7633c1b74290ebd89248a7","tid":1175632,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T18:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}